nodes.text: The Holopix News photographer assassin was a member of an unknown species. He was a member of the Assassin's Guild.

During Princess Leia Organa's first term as an Imperial senator, she was sent to the planet Challon. Emir hired the Assassin's Guild to assassinate Leia. This assassin impersonated a reporter from the Holopix News and attempted to assassinate Leia. Before he had the chance, Giles Durane and Gimlet killed him.
